            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> signum Mer<lb break="no" n="2"/>curi<surplus>o</surplus> et <expan><abbr>nume</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>|(denarios) |(mille) ut bb<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>ff</abbr><ex>iciarii</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>lega</abbr><ex>ti</ex></expan> de ussu<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> eorum <expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sportul</abbr><ex>as</ex></expan> accipiant <lb n="7"/>die <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> Ama<lb break="no" n="8"/>torius Pere<lb break="no" n="9"/>grinus <expan><abbr>veter</abbr><ex>anus</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>utrumque <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>onum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altarförmiger Sockel einer Merkurstatue. Z. 1 steht auf der corona. Z. 3: ET-Ligatur aus O verbessert. Z. 7: SPORTVLAS klein oberhalb der Zeile eingefügt. (B): Behrens, MZ 37/38: Z. 5-8 u. 12: Auflösung der Abkürzungen nicht gekennzeichnet.</p>
            </div>
